      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DESTINI REBEL (4) produced a modest effort most recently when fifth at Shepparton over 450m behind Ascend Igloo (27.23) in a Grade 5. Placed at his previous run. Can atone. NED THE KNIGHT (1) finds it hard to win but looks close to breaking through. Filled a minor placings again last time when third (26.31) at Shepparton making it three placings in a row. Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Expecting another good run. NOTORIOUS BLAZE (3) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Stella Rose (24.40) in a Bottom Up - Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. Leading player again. MOTIVATE (7) is worth consideration.",
